    "setup_instructions": {
      "value": "\n✅ AlphaLens Aurora Serverless v2 cluster deployed successfully!\n\nDatabase Details:\n- Cluster: alphalens-aurora-cluster\n- Database: alphalens\n- Data API: Enabled\n- Region: us-east-1\n\nAdd the following to alphalens/.env:\nAURORA_CLUSTER_ARN=arn:aws:rds:us-east-1:683872723714:cluster:alphalens-aurora-cluster\nAURORA_SECRET_ARN=arn:aws:secretsmanager:us-east-1:683872723714:secret:alphalens-aurora-credentials-7c3a0a01-GN3jAn\nDATABASE_NAME=alphalens\nDEFAULT_AWS_REGION=us-east-1\n\nTest the Data API connection:\naws rds-data execute-statement \\\n  --resource-arn arn:aws:rds:us-east-1:683872723714:cluster:alphalens-aurora-cluster \\\n  --secret-arn arn:aws:secretsmanager:us-east-1:683872723714:secret:alphalens-aurora-credentials-7c3a0a01-GN3jAn \\\n  --database alphalens \\\n  --region us-east-1 \\\n  --sql \"SELECT version()\"\n\nSet up the database schema (once migrations are implemented):\ncd alphalens/backend/database\nuv run run_migrations.py\n\n💰 Cost Management:\n- Current scaling: 0.5 - 1 ACUs\n- Estimated minimum: ~$43/month at 0.5 ACU\n- Destroy when not in use: cd alphalens/terraform/1_database \u0026\u0026 terraform destroy\n",
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
